PREP: Prepare chicken according to package directions. Combine lettuce, tomatoes, bacon, cheese and dressing. For each roll-up, heat one tortilla in microwave 20 seconds. Spread a line of guacamole down center of tortilla; place 2 cooked chicken tenders on tortilla; top with one-fourth of salad mix. Fold in sides of tortilla and roll up into cylinder shape. SERVE: Serve with tortilla chips and salsa, if desired. CHILL: Refrigerate leftovers immediately.